<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="251" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,506,1184,1247]" box="[151,361,1220,1247]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">
<figureCitation box="[151,279,1220,1247]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–18" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[160,1428,194,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-22@3.[160,1428,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 10–18. Longicornus brevispinus Fang &amp; Xing, 2019: 10. ♂, dorsal view; 11. ♂, lateral view; 12. ♂,face; Longicornus grossus sp. nov.: 13. ♂, dorsal view; 14. ♂, lateral view; 15. ♂,face; Longicornus longus Xing &amp; Li: 16. ♂, dorsal view; 17. ♂, lateral view; 18. ♂,face." pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Figs 13–15</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation box="[290,361,1220,1246]" captionStart-0="FIGURES 29–35" captionStart-1="FIGURES 36–41" captionStartId-0="4.[151,264,1966,1990]" captionStartId-1="5.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox-0="[237,1353,1051,1937]" captionTargetBox-1="[187,1399,198,1903]" captionTargetId-0="figure-88@4.[231,1357,1043,1943]" captionTargetId-1="figure-22@5.[172,1416,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId-0="4" captionTargetPageId-1="5" captionText-0="FIGURES 29–35. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 29. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 30. Valve, ventral view; 31. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 32. Aedeagus, lateral view; 33. Aedeagus, ventral view; 34. Connective, dorsal view; 35. Style, dorsal view." captionText-1="FIGURES 36–41. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 36. Genital capsule, lateral view; 37. Female seventh sternite, ventral view; 38. First valvula, lateral view; 39. Detail of sculptures of first valvula; 40. Second valvula, lateral view; 41. Detail of sculptures of second valaula." pageId="1" pageNumber="251">29–41</figureCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1292,1930]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,297,1292,1318]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Description.</emphasis>
Body short, robust and fuscous (
<figureCitation box="[663,746,1292,1318]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–18" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[160,1428,194,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-22@3.[160,1428,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 10–18. Longicornus brevispinus Fang &amp; Xing, 2019: 10. ♂, dorsal view; 11. ♂, lateral view; 12. ♂,face; Longicornus grossus sp. nov.: 13. ♂, dorsal view; 14. ♂, lateral view; 15. ♂,face; Longicornus longus Xing &amp; Li: 16. ♂, dorsal view; 17. ♂, lateral view; 18. ♂,face." pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Fig. 13</figureCitation>
). Vertex with paired irregular dark brown bands. Face marked with irregular yellowish brown lateral stripe (
<figureCitation box="[677,763,1328,1355]" captionStart="FIGURES 10–18" captionStartId="3.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[160,1428,194,1906]" captionTargetId="figure-22@3.[160,1428,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURES 10–18. Longicornus brevispinus Fang &amp; Xing, 2019: 10. ♂, dorsal view; 11. ♂, lateral view; 12. ♂,face; Longicornus grossus sp. nov.: 13. ♂, dorsal view; 14. ♂, lateral view; 15. ♂,face; Longicornus longus Xing &amp; Li: 16. ♂, dorsal view; 17. ♂, lateral view; 18. ♂,face." pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Fig. 15</figureCitation>
). Forewing dark brown, with scatered hyaline areas (Figs. 13,14). Legs brownish, with dark bands.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1292,1930]" box="[199,677,1400,1427]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">External features as in generic description.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1292,1930]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">
<emphasis box="[199,371,1436,1462]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Male genitalia.</emphasis>
Subgenital plate with 6 setae along lateral margin (
<figureCitation box="[949,1033,1436,1462]" captionStart="FIGURES 29–35" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1966,1990]" captionTargetBox="[237,1353,1051,1937]" captionTargetId="figure-88@4.[231,1357,1043,1943]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 29–35. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 29. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 30. Valve, ventral view; 31. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 32. Aedeagus, lateral view; 33. Aedeagus, ventral view; 34. Connective, dorsal view; 35. Style, dorsal view." pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Fig. 31</figureCitation>
). Aedeagal shaft short and robust in ventral view, aedeagus with pair of furcate processes with one branch approximately as long as shaft and extended distad, other branch shorter than half length of shaft and extended posterad (
<figureCitation box="[1005,1141,1508,1534]" captionStart="FIGURES 29–35" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1966,1990]" captionTargetBox="[237,1353,1051,1937]" captionTargetId="figure-88@4.[231,1357,1043,1943]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 29–35. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 29. Male pygofer side, lateral view; 30. Valve, ventral view; 31. Subgenital plate, ventral view; 32. Aedeagus, lateral view; 33. Aedeagus, ventral view; 34. Connective, dorsal view; 35. Style, dorsal view." pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Figs. 32, 33</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1292,1930]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">
Female seventh sternite approximately as long as broad at base, caudal margin medially produced (
<figureCitation box="[1338,1424,1544,1570]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–41" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[187,1399,198,1903]" captionTargetId="figure-22@5.[172,1416,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 36–41. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 36. Genital capsule, lateral view; 37. Female seventh sternite, ventral view; 38. First valvula, lateral view; 39. Detail of sculptures of first valvula; 40. Second valvula, lateral view; 41. Detail of sculptures of second valaula." pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Fig. 37</figureCitation>
). Female pygofer with ventroposterior margin slightly incurved. (
<figureCitation box="[894,982,1580,1607]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–41" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[187,1399,198,1903]" captionTargetId="figure-22@5.[172,1416,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 36–41. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 36. Genital capsule, lateral view; 37. Female seventh sternite, ventral view; 38. First valvula, lateral view; 39. Detail of sculptures of first valvula; 40. Second valvula, lateral view; 41. Detail of sculptures of second valaula." pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Fig. 36</figureCitation>
). First valvulae with obscure reticulate sculpture dorsally and scale-like sculpture ventrally (
<figureCitation box="[745,883,1616,1642]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–41" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[187,1399,198,1903]" captionTargetId="figure-22@5.[172,1416,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 36–41. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 36. Genital capsule, lateral view; 37. Female seventh sternite, ventral view; 38. First valvula, lateral view; 39. Detail of sculptures of first valvula; 40. Second valvula, lateral view; 41. Detail of sculptures of second valaula." pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Figs. 38, 39</figureCitation>
). Second valvulae with some distal teeth occupying about half of the total length (
<figureCitation box="[527,664,1652,1678]" captionStart="FIGURES 36–41" captionStartId="5.[151,264,1943,1967]" captionTargetBox="[187,1399,198,1903]" captionTargetId="figure-22@5.[172,1416,181,1919]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 36–41. Longicornus grossus sp. nov. 36. Genital capsule, lateral view; 37. Female seventh sternite, ventral view; 38. First valvula, lateral view; 39. Detail of sculptures of first valvula; 40. Second valvula, lateral view; 41. Detail of sculptures of second valaula." pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Figs. 40, 41</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,1292,1930]" box="[199,969,1688,1715]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,371,1688,1714]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251">Measurement.</emphasis>
Length (including tegmen): 
<specimenCount box="[686,705,1688,1715]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
5.6 mm, 
<specimenCount box="[806,820,1688,1715]" pageId="1" pageNumber="251" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
5.7–5.9 mm.
</paragraph>
